title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-20-2013 WED
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-20-2013 WED


Wednesday, November 20, 2013


Eco-Fascism
 
 

 - 9AM hour

President Obama leaves out "under God" from his rendition of the Gettysburg Address

     requested by Ken Burns.
                              Why did Burns send a version without the phrase?



 - 10AM hour

Guest: James Delingpole, author of, 

                       "The Little Green Book of Eco-Fascism."



 - 11AM hour

1. Recall of Edie Hudak. 

2. Leftists in the Northwest wants government to takeover Boeing and retool them for mass transit.

 3. Fukushima nuclear plant discussion.
